text: Irina Izmalkova (born 21 June 1970) is a Russian sport shooter. She participated at the 2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships, winning a medal.10 m team running target results ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1970 births Category:Russian female sport shooters Category:Running target shooters Category:Sportspeople from Volgograd
